self.movies[1]['country'] = 'USA'
response = self.app.patch('/%s/actors/%s/movies/%s' % (self.api, self.
    actors[1]['id'], self.movies[1]['id']), headers=self.headers, data=json
    .dumps({'country': 'USA'}), content_type='application/json')
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 204)
response = self.app.get('/%s/movies/%s' % (self.api, self.movies[1]['id']),
    headers=self.headers)
response_json = json.loads(response.data)
self.assertEqual(self.movies[1], response_json)
